CELEBRATING TCO’S 30 YEAR ANNIVERSARY WITH ATYRAU RESIDENTS Yesterday, we had the great pleasure of celebrating along with the thousands of Atyrau city residents, the company’s 30th Anniversary. The Deputy City Governor, Nurzhan Ermukhanov, commended the partnership between the regional government and TCO, to support the region’s socio-economic development. Kevin Lyon TCO’s General Director, noted that the company’s success over the last three decades, would not have been possible without the support of the local residents. It was a festive atmosphere and an uplifting event that will surely remain in memories for a long time to come! Similar concerts were held in Kulsary city and at the Tengiz field for our workforce. #kazakhstan #tco #chevron #partnership
